version_description:
- In the Access app you can now see which service you are logging into. For your security, always check whether it is the service that you want.

- Ongoing improvements and minor error corrections

• Easy to activate: Activate the Access app without a registration key and start using it immediately
• Various devices: Use the app on multiple devices, such as smartphones and tablets
• Additional access authorization: You can also use the app with more than one e-banking agreement number
• Forgotten PIN: Change it by reactivating the access authorization

Ongoing improvements and minor error corrections: There is a new "Messages" area in the UBS Access app where you will soon be able to securely confirm your online purchases by credit / prepaid card. We will also provide you with information about security-related events.
